\f3\b\fs28 \cf2 Phase\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf2 The phase between LRCLK and BCLK is critical of all surveyed CODECs and DACs, and is managed directly within a single PIO state machine.\
MCLK to BCLK phase is not critical, but should not shift over time. This is achieved by having related PIO clocks for the LRCLK/BCLK and MCLK state machines.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

